spinner

  Shows an animated cursor while waiting for a particular program to exit.


Dead-simple example

     { some && long && command ; } & ; spinner $!


Arguments

   pid  # of process to wait for.  Required.


Exit codes

   0    process we're waiting for ended, hurray.
   1    pid never existed.
 else   error


